name: Jatiluwih 259 Restaurant dan Homestay
address: Banjar Soka, Senganan, Kec. Penebel, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82152, Indonesia
review 1: I love this place a lot. Located in a beautiful area of Jatiluwih village, you can enjoy your meal with great atmosphere. You can take pictures around the place while waiting for the food to be served.
review 2: Today stopped by with friends, great place, beautiful views of rice fields and mountains, comfortable atmosphere, good food, standard prices.  nice to relax
review 3: Such a cozy place to spend days in bali with paddy field view all the way to the top of the mountain of batukaru
review 4:
Best Ice Lemongrass Tea of Bali ❤️

Pizza was good, but we loved the drink.
review 5: Friendly service, nice place for gathering, reasonable price, karaoke

name: Warung nyoam campuhan sari
address: Jl. Batu Luwih Kawan No.37, Senganan, Kec. Penebel, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82152, Indonesia
review 1:
Great little place!
Fair prices and tasty food.
Much cheaper than warung 259 down the road and real local food.
review 3:
Stopped here on our way to jatiluwih, ate some very nice mie goreng with chicken for a good price (35k IDR), with a very nice view over the rice fields. The staff was very friendly and told/showed us a lot about the area and how they processed rice from the plantations. Afterwards we had a flat tire on the scooter, the staff was very helpful and proposed to take the motorbike to the mechanic and get it fixed. We didn't even need to pay for it which was so kind.
After all a very positive experience!
review 4: The food was ok, the rice was good but the egg too oily. Great view and the owner was very friendly. He gave us free passion fruit from his trees, very good.
review 5: Beautiful view, delicious food. Owner is a local organic rice farmer who is full of information and knowledge and smiles.  Well worth the stop.
